OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading this evening to leave a mostly
OL,7,Fdry night with clear spells. Patchy
OL,8,Ffog and frost reforming. However,
OL,9,Fcloudier and windier conditions with
OL,10,Frain arriving across many southwestern
OL,11,Fparts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTuesday will be cloudy and
OL,14,Frather windy in the west and southwest
OL,15,Fwith further rain and some fog
OL,16,Fpatches. Mostly dry elsewhere with
OL,17,Flighter winds and warm spells of
OL,18,Fsunshine.
